title: Lena Dunham Is Not That Kind of Girl
description: Well folks. This week at book club we learn that Lena Dunham wrote a book. It was full of essays. She makes some points and misses a lot of points and we do our best to sift through the rubble. Tees are Here!! Grab a Worm Tee or an Unhinged Tee here: https://celebritymemoirbookclub.square.site/Follow us on Twitter @cmbc_podcast and Instagram @celebritymemoirbookclub If you want even more juice subscribe to our patreon!!! This week we’re talking to @kardashian_kolloquium about the Kardashian reunion special!!!https://www.patreon.com/celebritymemoirbookclub Art by @adrianne_manpearl and theme song by @ashleesimpsonrossSupport the show
